name: Men's "King County" Tee
description:
**LIMITED QUANTITIES**

Very proud of our first t-shirt, the Sir Charles Barkley "King County" tee!  Artwork done by the talented Anthony Do (antqdo.com), representing "Sir Charles" and our home of King County. 

DESCRIPTION:
100% Deluxe combed ring-spun cotton. Featuring a ¾” Set-in collar, double-needle bottom hem and sleeves with shoulder-to-shoulder tape. Pre-shrunk to minimize shrinkage. Slightly slimmer fit. 

SPECS:
Body Width: 
S=18"
M=20"
L=22"
XL=24"

CARE:
Machine wash cold with like colors.  Hang dry to minimize shrinkage. Do not iron on the image.

SHIPPING:
Free. U.S. only.  Will ship in 4-6 business days.

RETURN POLICY:
No returns or exchanges.  Please double check your order information and shipping address before submitting to ensure you get the correct item.
